    """
    Compute the semantic signature of the current string state.

    Returns:
        (n, signature) where:
          - n = length of minimal closed walk (assuming self.phase encodes S)
          - signature = [Δu_2, Δu_3, ..., Δu_m], m = argmin{k | u_k = n}
